CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 13, 1952, pg. 27 reads: "Golfdom's Best - Being average wasn't good enough at the South Park golf course last week as the above champions proved in annexing UGA crowns...Russell Nalle, far right, won his second straight crown in Men's Senior Division - Teenie Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Russell Nalle wearing eyeglasses, striped hat, and geometrically patterned shirt, holding golf club to golf ball on South Park golf course for UGA tournament
